high_descs: Turn to the right and move towards the range, then turn to the right and move to the dishwasher in front of the window.
Pick up the gray patterned plate from the counter to the left of the toaster and in front of the window.
Turn to the left and then move to and face the range.
Open the microwave above the range, place the plate on top of the plate in the microwave, microwave both plates, then open up the microwave and remove the gray patterned plate.
Turn around and move towards the kitchen door then turn left and move to the black table in the corner.
Place the gray patterned plate on the table between the gray plate and the blue bowl.
